sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>API: GET /api/batches?page=1&limit=20
    API->>API: Extract device fingerprint
    API->>DB: Find User by fingerprint
    
    alt User not found
        DB-->>API: null
        API-->>U: { batches: [], pagination: {...} }
    else User found
        DB-->>API: User record
        API->>DB: Query ScanBatch WHERE user_id = ?
        DB-->>API: List of batches
        API->>API: Calculate pagination
        API-->>U: { batches: [...], pagination: {...} }
    end
